# Firmware images, partition dumps, and binaries must NEVER get EOL/text conversion.
# (LF->CRLF mangling of binary dumps is exactly what corrupts preloader/userdata backups.)
*.img    binary
*.bin    binary
*.gz     binary
*.lz4    binary
*.zst    binary
*.br     binary
*.xz     binary
*.zip    binary
*.so     binary
*.dll    binary
*.exe    binary
*.pem    -text
*.payload binary
*.scatter binary
